      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "Selection panels present a list of codes which may be entered in the"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "COMMAND/OPTION field and selected by pressing the ENTER key.  The code"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "is normally a single digit or a single letter.  Allowable codes are"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "listed in high intensity on each selection panel.  SPF/PC commands may"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "also be entered in the COMMAND/OPTION field."
      },
      {
        "type": "blank"
      },
      {
        "type": "field_row",
        "fields": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "content": "Note: If the code"
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "content": "blank+is listed, leave the COMMAND/OPTION field blank and"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "press ENTER to select that option (do not type the characters \"blank\")."
